---

<Layout title="About - Dan Morris">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-900 to-purple-900 rounded-lg p-8 mb-12">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">About Me</h1>
      <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed">
        Hi, I'm Dan Morris, a seasoned Lead System Architect with a passion for turning complex challenges into 
        elegant, scalable solutions. With over 15 years in the field, I've mastered the art of building robust 
        systems that seamlessly integrate sophisticated backend architectures with intuitive frontend experiences.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
      <div class="bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md border border-gray-700">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-blue-400">Professional Journey</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          Throughout my extensive career, I've collaborated with a diverse portfolio of organizations, from 
          innovative startups to industry-leading enterprises. My expertise spans multiple domains, including 
          high-performance media processing systems, immersive theme park experiences, and sophisticated 
          embedded solutions.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md border border-gray-700">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-purple-400">Philosophy</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          I'm driven by the belief that technology should empower and enhance human capabilities. My approach 
          blends technical innovation with pragmatic problem-solving, delivering solutions that are not only 
          cutting-edge but also sustainable and impactful. I strive to create systems that make a meaningful 
          difference in how people work and interact with technology.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Areas of Expertise</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        {expertise.map(item => (
          <div class="bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md border border-gray-700">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
              <span class="text-3xl mr-3">{item.icon}</span>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-100">{item.area}</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-300">{item.description}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Professional Experience</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        {experience.map(item => (
          <div class="bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md border border-gray-700">
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start md:items-center mb-4">
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-400">{item.role}</h3>
                <p class="text-purple-400 font-medium">{item.company}</p>
                {item.location && <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">{item.location}</p>}
              </div>
              <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium mt-2 md:mt-0">{item.year}</span>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-2 mt-4">
              {item.highlights.map(highlight => {
                const isIndented = highlight.startsWith('-');
                const displayText = isIndented ? highlight.substring(2) : highlight;
                return (
                  <li class={`flex items-start ${isIndented ? 'ml-12' : ''}`}>
                    <span class="text-blue-400 mr-2">‚Ä∫</span>
                    <span class="text-gray-300">{displayText}</span>
                  </li>
                );
              })}
            </ul>
            {item.technologies && (
              <div class="mt-4">
                <h4 class="text-gray-200 font-semibold mb-2">Technologies:</h4>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                  {item.technologies.map(tech => (
                    <span class="bg-gray-700 text-blue-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">
                      {tech}
                    </span>
                  ))}
                </div>
              </div>
            )}
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Core Values</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        {values.map(value => (
          <div class="bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md border border-gray-700">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-blue-400">{value.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300">{value.description}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md border border-gray-700 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Let's Work Together</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">
        I'm always eager to take on new challenges and collaborate on innovative projects. 
        Whether you're seeking technical expertise, architectural guidance, or a strategic technology partner,
        I'd love to help transform your vision into reality. Let's create something exceptional together.
      </p>
